headline.main: RUMANIANS HOPE TO DROP WAR ROLE; Many of Occupation Troops in Russia Expect to Go Home Soon With Task Done

lead_paragraph: WITH RUMANIAN ARMY OF OCCUPATION, at Ochakov, on Black Sea, Oct. 20 (delayed) (AP) -- Rumanian troops stationed in this area believe the Russian war is over as far as they are concerned.
abstract: Odessa damage reptd heavy; German divers try to retrieve arms sunk in Black Sea by retreating USSR forces; early discharge of Rumanian troops from fighting seen; Rumanian penetration limited to Bug River; only 3 corps slated to remain to aid Axis fighting armies
